displayName: customer v1
description: Cannonical customer
type: object
properties:
  metadata:
    type: object
    properties:
      version:
         type: string
         minLength: 1
         maxLength: 5
         required: true
         pattern: "1.0.0"
         description: |
           The version of the cannonical model schema.
      origin:
        type: string
        required: true
        enum: [ comsas, capital, sonata, acurity ]
        description: |
          The name of the administration system that the data originated from.
      date_created:
        type: number?
        required: false
        displayName: date created
        description: |
          The date created represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
      date_last_modified:
        type: number?
        required: false
        displayName: date last modified
        description: |
          The date last modified represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
  identifiers:
    type: object
    properties:
      internal:
        required: true
        type: object
        properties:
          primary:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            description: |
              The unique identifier of the record in the origin system.
      external:
        type: object
        required: false
        properties:
          master_index:
            type: bson_object_identifier?
            required: false
            description: |
              The identifier of the customer in the master index.
  attributes:
    type: object
    required: true
    properties:
      name:
        type: object
        properties:
          title:
            type: string?
            required: false
            description: |
              An honorific prefix preceding a Person's name. For example Dr, Mrs, or Mr.
          rank:
            type: string?
            required: false
            description: |
              A current military rank preceding a Person's name. For example Captain.
          given:
            type: string?
            required: false
            description: |
              The first name of a Person. For example John.
          middle:
            type: string?
            required: false
            description: |
              An additional name for a Person. For example Matthew.
          family:
            type: string
            required: false
            description: |
              The last name of a Person. For example Doe.
      birth_date:
        type: date-only?
        required: false
        displayName: birth date
        description: |
          The date of birth for a Person. For Example 2000-01-01.
      death_date:
        type: date-only?
        required: false
        displayName: death date
        description: |
          The date of death for a Person. For Example 2000-01-01.
      sex:
        type: string
        enum: [male, female]
        required: false
        description: |
          The sex of a Person as defined at birth.
      gender:
        type: string?
        required: false
        description: |
           The prefered gender of a Person.
      tax_file_numbers:
        type: array
        required: true
        displayName: tax file numbers
        items:
          type: string
          pattern: "[0-9]{9}"

displayName: address v1
description: Cannonical address
type: object
properties:
  metadata:
    type: object
    properties:
      version:
         type: string
         minLength: 1
         maxLength: 5
         required: true
         pattern: "1.0.0"
         description: |
           The version of the cannonical model schema.
      origin:
        type: string
        enum: [ comsas, capital, sonata, acurity ]
        description: |
          The name of the administration system that the data originated from.
      date_created:
        type: number?
        displayName: date created
        description: |
          The date created represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
      date_last_modified:
        type: number?
        displayName: date last modified
        description: |
          The date last modified represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
  identifiers:
    type: object
    properties:
      internal:
        type: object
        properties:
          primary:
            type: string?
            description: |
              The unique identifier of the record in the origin system.
          customer:
            type: string
            minLength: 1
            description: |
              The identifier of the customer in the origin system.
      external:
        type: object
        required: false
        properties:
          master_index:
            type: bson_object_identifier
            required: false
            description: |
              The identifier of the customer in the master index.
  attributes:
    type: object
    properties:
        kind:
          type: string
          enum: [ business, tty, alternate business, alternate fax, home, fax, residential, mobile ]
          description: |
            The kind of telephone number.
        country_code:
          type: string?
          required: false
          displayName: country code
          description: |
            The country code of a telephone number. For example +61.
        area_code:
          type: string?
          required: false
          displayName: country code
          description: |
            The area code of a telephone number. For example 04.
        subscriber_number:
          type: string?
          required: false
          displayName: country code
          description: |
            The subscriber number of a telephone number. For example 2345678.
        current:
          type: boolean
          required: true
          description: |
            A boolean value indicating whether this record is set as the Customers current telephone number.

type: string
pattern: "[A-F|a-f|0-9]{24}"
displayName: BSON identifier

type: object
displayName: Interest v1
description: Cannonical interest v1
properties:
  metadata:
    type: object
    properties:
       version:
          type: string
          minLength: 1
          maxLength: 5
          required: true
          pattern: "1.0.0"
          description: |
            The version of the cannonical model schema
       origin:
         type: string
         enum: [ comsas, capital, sonata, acurity ]
         description: |
           The name of the administration system that the data originated from.
       date_created:
         type: number?
         required: false
         displayName: date created
         description: |
           The date created represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
       date_last_modified:
         type: number?
         required: false
         displayName: date last modified
         description: |
           The date last modified represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
  identifiers:
    type: object
    properties:
       internal:
         type: object
         properties:
            primary:
                 type: string
                 required: true
                 minLength: 1
                 description: |
                   The unique identifier of the record in the origin system.
            customer:
                 type: string
                 required: true
                 description: |
                   The identifier of the customer in the origin system.
       external:
         type: object
         properties:
             primary:
                 type: string
                 required: true
                 minLength: 1
                 description: |
                   The identifier of the interest known to the customer.
             master_index:
                 type: bson_object_identifier?
                 required: false
                 description: |
                   The identifier of the customer in the master index.
  attributes:
    type: object
    properties:
       scheme:
          type: string
          required: true
          enum: [ css, pss, '1922', png, dfrb, dfrdb, msbs, adfc ]
          description: |
            The scheme that the interest belongs too.
       kind:
          type: string
          enum: [ subsumed, preserved, pension, contributing, no equity, deleted, re-entered member, preserver, mbl pension, transferred, contributor, cancelled/reversed, ancillary member, non-contributing, associate, 40 years, ancillary spouse, mbl - lump sum, contributor pension, child pension, orphan pension, pension, member pension, unknown ]
          required: true
          minLength: 1
          description: |
            The kind of interest.
       status:
          type: string
          required: false
          enum: [ exited, current, cancelled, unknown ]
          description: |
            The status of an interest.
       start_date:
          type: number
          required: false
          displayName: start date
          description: |
            The start date represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
       end_date:
          type: number?
          required: false
          displayName: end date
          description: |
            The end date represented as the number of milliseconds since epoch.
